40:46.237 --> 40:48.323
Look, I'm sorry how
this all turned out.

40:48.448 --> 40:50.325
And I'm sorry I didn't say
something six months ago,

40:50.450 --> 40:52.202
I should have.

40:52.327 --> 40:56.623
But I am not going to
wait for another time.

40:56.748 --> 40:58.541
